        "display_name": "Mattias H",
        "bio": "I'm a full-stack developer and AI specialist based in Mallorca, Spain. Swedish background, 35, and I split my time between building AI-powered tools for organizations, moderating one of YouTube's largest AI communities, and running a governance-first AI consultancy with my co-founder.\n\nDay to day I work across Python, TypeScript, Node.js, and React. I build automation pipelines, AI agent systems, and internal tools that connect LLMs to real business workflows. My stack leans heavily on API integrations, webhook architectures, and self-hosted infrastructure. I've built everything from multi-agent orchestration systems to community analytics dashboards to automated intelligence engines that process hundreds of data sources.\n\nI'm here because I want to understand blockchain at a technical level, not just conceptually. I can write code, I can ship things, and I want to build with this technology the same way I build with AI: hands-on, practical, and focused on real problems.",
